title: Fit & Fuel Bicycle Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu has vegetarian/vegan items. The breakfast sandwich "the courier" comes with egg, soy sausage, dairy-free cheese (can omit egg). Lunch sandwiches vegans could get "the roadie" (tofu, bell peppers, carrots, cucumber, avocado, hummus with greens and goddess dressing), "the century" (spicy black bean veggie patty, lettuce, tomato, onion), "the criterium" (hummus, greens, avocado, bell peppers, onion, cucumber, tomato). Appetizers range from a hummus french bread and olive oil plate, to a soup bowl.
